00076 typedef enum {
00077         // Types for audio formats:
00078         sptPCMU = 0,        
00079         firstStaticPayloadType = sptPCMU,
00080         // 1016 static payload type is now deprecated. Type 1 is reserved.
00081         // spt1016,         ///< CELP audio (FED-STD 1016) (RFC 1890)

00083         sptGSM,

00095         sptG728,            
00096         sptDVI4_11025,      
00097         sptDVI4_22050,      
00098         sptG729,            
00099         // Type 19 is reserved. Types 20 - 23 are unassigned.
00100         lastStaticAudioPayloadType = sptG729,
00101 
00102         // Types for video formats:

00104         sptCELB = 25,

00111         sptMP2T,            
00112         sptH263,            
00113         // Types 35 - 71 are unassigned.
00114         // Types 72 - 76 are reserved.
00115         // Types 96 - 127 are dynamic.
00116         lastStaticPayloadType = sptH263
